Package gitlet

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Dumpable
    An interface describing dumpable objects.
    Hashable
    A hashable object
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Blob
    A Blob that saves files
    Branch
    A named Branch that saves a line of commits
    Commit
    A commit that saves files for that commit, a commit message and datetime, as well as its parents
    DumpObj
    A debugging class whose main program may be invoked as follows: java gitlet.DumpObj FILE...
    Main
    Driver class for Gitlet, the tiny stupid version-control system.
    Manager
    Manages the state of the git repo as a whole: the staging area, all of the branches, the current branch
    Savable<T extends Savable>
    A savable (serializable) object
    Savable.SavableList<T extends Savable>
    Essentially just a list of pointer objects of a given type
    Savable.SavablePointer<T extends Savable>
    Pointer to an object.
    StagingArea
    Staging area that contains a list of staged files
    UnitTest
    The suite of all JUnit tests for the gitlet package.
    Utils
    Assorted utilities.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    GitletException
    General exception indicating a Gitlet error.
